Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這股奇怪的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隱約覺得這城市的氣氛有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們進城開始 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棺引人注目?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 他們是在看你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你長相打扮是挺顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可又不是從沒見過年輕女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一個年輕女性都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是用於機杖的粉末化石思念料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這點?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賣給您的只有這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此地 化石思念料產地 產量維馬克王國第一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說 這伊貝克市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是加瓦爾尼公爵領最大的化石思念料市場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持有現金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我庫存不多 除去本地要用的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賣給外來者的只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近收獲量減少了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這倒沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 最近領主大人徵收的數量驟增…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領主…加瓦爾尼公爵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼需要那麼多呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 總之這些就是所有的量了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我在街上完全看不到年輕女性的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼特殊原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵大人每隔幾天就會派人帶走城裡少女回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派他的直屬軍隊來 半強制性地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行帶走?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被帶走的女孩再沒有回來過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生是死都還是未知數…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還有人害怕得試圖逃出城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但聽說都被抓住 給殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你們也盡快離開較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不准什麼時候「少女狩獵」就又要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若在我這爭鬥起來 小店也承受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 付賬咱們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒人去宅邸探望一下女孩們的情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為公爵大人現在的宅邸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔天際的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是這裡領主的城堡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞索厄拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是賈茲帝國首都攻防戰時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維馬克王國派出的兩座要塞之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在因受到魔法攻擊而返回的途中 緊急迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就順勢推給了加瓦爾尼領進行管理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而加瓦爾尼擅自進行了修理 乘上它到處飛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那領主到底在想些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜集化石思念料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來也是為了驅動那大得要命的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且還掠走一大堆女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是有夠蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 這也使那個傳聞增添了一份可信度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果加瓦爾尼公爵入手賈茲皇帝的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的理由原本是個謎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若是為了用作魔力源 驅動航天要塞…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實說得通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之既然有傳聞說他持有遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就有必要進去確認下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能用魔法來飛上天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難 專用機杖 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 只能再去拜託那傢伙了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你就願意和我打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要等從那成功回收了遺體之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對 我們說定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 約定 重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要與不死身裝鎧龍幹架呢 不能為我著想一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不死身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被破壞了腦部還是會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我先得掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺兄長請便 但我還要製成標本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要留下太大傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自商量個什麼呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡 繼續靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體 定在裡面 我確信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 阿卡莉 突入突入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我講過這次只是來探查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查清楚了再說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到合適的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真能輕鬆被突入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說不上是什麼要塞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 突入趕緊地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到剛才說進不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長 怎辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子這東西只能從內側打開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內側…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾民傾聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵宅聘請傭人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為公爵效勞的人 立即站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為公爵效勞的人 站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是加瓦爾尼公爵家顧問魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛拉特·藍斯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先到別間等候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細指示稍候再予以通知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是倉庫和空房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令室在更上面?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 從構造上來講應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知公爵是否也在那兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然越往上戒備越森嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行衝上去?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著急不得啊 薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們多花些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交份詳盡的報告書給基烈特大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初使者被殺時 就該派兵強攻挫掉對方的銳氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再磨蹭下去 加瓦爾尼公爵都要攻到這卡德威爾來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我的部下正在收集情報及確認情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在報告傳來之前還請再給一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪還有這份閒空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應盡快編制討伐部隊 以最大兵力進行討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 事已至此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力制裁也是迫不得已的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 請下決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命聯軍以航天要塞史特拉托斯為中心組成討伐軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對加瓦爾尼公爵進行討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定期聯絡 關於航天要塞索厄拉的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞內部除偶有士兵巡邏外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎沒有人的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出奇的安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加瓦爾尼公爵自我們潛入以來還從沒有現身過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體統管要塞事務的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是自稱葛拉特·藍斯亞的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有一次見到名貴族打扮的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與葛拉特·藍斯亞在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是加瓦爾尼公爵的親屬?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我們一起進來的女性們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被轉移到休息室後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被分成了幾波人 移動到了別處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加瓦爾尼公爵的真意何在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到底是為何驅動這航天要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將繼續調查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇·荷羅派涅 芷依塔·布魯薩斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康拉德機關長傳來緊急通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特隊長 事情不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗登 隨同部隊準備如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣隊已出發前往加瓦爾尼領
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只待閣下的號令了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻起我航天要塞史特拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及西方第六軍團 將出發討伐逆賊加瓦爾尼公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的要塞也正因喜悅而顫抖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動史特拉托斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖有盡力勸阻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但未能推翻決定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討伐部隊將於明早抵達加瓦爾尼領
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你潛入索厄拉的兩名隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請你轉達消息 讓她們想辦法自行逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了啊 小梟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願她們兩人能平安逃離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在那無處可逃的天上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地…小心點飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 慎重 重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很準時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 問題無?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡 侵入成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是武器庫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內部情形探查得怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶沒什麼有價值的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該在上面有司令室的階層
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞的支柱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能 機杖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機杖? 這麼大隻?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞 驅動 機杖 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力 巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機杖 巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得要吃那麼多化石思念料了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上這個能一口氣到上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可若到站就被圍住 那就成甕中之鱉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有其他路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉 分頭行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還跑得動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 不過裝鎧龍自帶治癒能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點小傷死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都明白目標是遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要往上走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總能在哪遇上芙蕾多妮卡和阿卡莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是覺得剛才那幫士兵不太尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋常 不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作出奇的整齊劃一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且受到攻擊別說痛叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連吃痛的表現都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣? 能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然型號有些舊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能否趁這騷亂 潛去上面調查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你想幫到基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要謹慎行事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次情況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前兩人獨處時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣…我說了才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定期聯絡的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還沒到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠抓到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鬧得挺歡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這最後關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混進來了些有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到入侵者了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里加爾圖·加瓦爾尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加瓦爾尼公爵的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我是最小的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是受聯合國指示闖進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼說 人數也太少了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 只是探查情況的密探嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:17:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們派過來的使者 變成了什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解體亂破師我還是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心臟 是什麼顏色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別喜歡切割人的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細緻肢解得四分五裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要問我理由 我也答不上來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惡趣味的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想看看你父母長啥樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你指加瓦爾尼公爵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見不到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論父親還是母親 哥哥還是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經分解掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里加爾圖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩身體素質很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥本領也很高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得利用她追捕入侵者較為合適
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 現在是關鍵時刻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是主謀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際驅動這座要塞的是葛拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三人 只是目的相同才一起行動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要請你去幫忙抓捕同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 用力吸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想用魔法控制人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須侵入精神 時刻進行控制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那遠遠不夠完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能設置命令的中繼點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將人在保持人格的狀態下進行操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼即使控制整支軍隊也不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ulu suei innu turun im contu naikt muei
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Luwai ulkait ennu ortz zuin kohku Nahl auyu atsuro sib tolug
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我完成的魔法術式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應感到榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧 奪取服從者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉 令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 得盡快匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜得讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對我們是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想稍微到房間外看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被帶來的女孩之一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮的人 強制帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小偷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從外面進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 有從這裡出去的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請帶我們逃離這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好幾人也被抓來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 救出請求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣把要做的事做了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先帶我們去你們被抓的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這裡近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞史特拉托斯出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將於明早發動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩幾個小時 要我們怎麼逃離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是天上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說若我們逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得和這索厄拉共存亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國的軍隊差不多該往這邊來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會派航天要塞出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這毋庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊也將馬上做好出擊的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻終於要到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的夢想 成為現實的時候要到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉也會高興的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 蕾拉也會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用這個下去 就到大家那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 還要下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趁現在快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們留在這裡 只會拖他後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞內
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知的可怕事實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我困惑至極
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯與阿卡莉 是否平安?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周 第十一集 「假公主」
